# astromech
A Python library for interfacing with Galaxy's Edge Astromech Droids

![alt text](images/r2t2.jpg "Title")

# Quickstart
```
cd astromech
python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt

export PYTHONPATH=.
python samples/r2.py
```
